- Design reputation tracking and trust scoring system
- Define F2F (friend-to-friend) connection model
- Specify trust propagation and path calculation
- Document privacy and security considerations
- Plan tool integration with Graphiti Wall plugin

## Acceptance Criteria

- [x] Design document created covering trust model overview
